em/raw-responsive-photography-wordpress-theme/5965864\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/raw.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Raw WordPress Theme is a fully responsive HTML5 theme that is ideal for photographers, agencies and creative freelancers. It offers several homepage layout options, full and fixed width portfolio grids, awesome hover effects, full width sliders with HTML5 background video &#038; touch support, fashionable captions, contact form with honeypot spam prevention and tons of professional styling options</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/raw-responsive-photography-wordpress-theme/5965864\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Raw theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">Erovo theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/erovo-responsive-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/9342804\"><img src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/erovo.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Responsive Multipurpose WordPress theme</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/erovo-responsive-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/9342804\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Erovo theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">Insignia Theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/insignia-flexible-opencart-theme/5563201\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/insignia.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Insignia is powerful, configurable and responsive HTML5 OpenCart theme. It’s good choice for any kind of store. It has built in Blog manager module, Revolution Slider, MegaMenu functionality and theme configurator which will help you to customize Your shop as you want.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/insignia-flexible-opencart-theme/5563201\">Purchase Insignia theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">Everal Theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://cohhe.com/project-view/everal/\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/everal.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Free and clean, modern, user friendly, responsive and customizable theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://cohhe.com/project-view/everal/\">Download Everal Theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">PayPal for WooCommerce</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://www.angelleye.com/product/paypal-for-woocommerce-plugin/\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/paypalforwoo.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Millions of shoppers pay with PayPal. If you already accept credit cards online, you can also accept PayPal by adding our Express Checkout button—and boost sales by up to 18% in the process.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://www.angelleye.com/product/paypal-for-woocommerce-plugin/\">Download PayPal for WooCommerce</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=JIpq9DJVKk4:UHinlBO-v2s:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=JIpq9DJVKk4:UHinlBO-v2s:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=JIpq9DJVKk4:UHinlBO-v2s:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://fe