n','open','','display-feed','','','2012-07-31 20:49:10','2012-07-31 20:49:10','',0,'http://themes.tielabs.com/365news/?page_id=162',0,'page','',0),(165,1,'2012-07-31 20:49:56','2012-07-31 20:49:56','','Contact','','publish','closed','closed','','sitemap','','','2014-09-11 09:52:12','2014-09-11 09:52:12','',0,'http://themes.tielabs.com/365news/?page_id=165',0,'page','',0),(223,1,'2012-08-02 09:07:15','2012-08-02 09:07:15','<h4><span style=\"color: #008000;\">PROGRAMME APPROACHES</span></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Livelihoods diversification for the farmer villagers in the programme’s geographical focuses to\r\ncreate more income sources for the farmers and therefore, reduce their vulnerability to few main\r\ncrops, and to risks in nature and society.</li>\r\n	<li>Participatory approach in combination with grassroots democracy promotion to create active\r\nresponses from the local people in development from planning, implementing, monitoring,\r\nevaluation and reporting of their local development plans at village and commune level;</li>\r\n	<li>Farmer-to-farmer approach to strengthen capacity of key farmers who will work as nuclear\r\nreaction agents for spreading technical production and management knowledge and improving\r\nrelated skills.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><span style=\"color: #008000;\">DEVELOPMENT FOCUS</span></h4>\r\nThe CSEED programme focuses on livelihoods and environment.\r\n<h5><span style=\"color: #008000;\"> In livelihoods, CSEED focuses on 3 main sectors:</span></h5>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Agriculture/Food sovereignty</li>\r\n	<li>Non-farm production</li>\r\n	<li>Forestry</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h5><span style=\"color: #008000;\"> In environment, we focus on:</span></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Disaster preparedness, climate change adaptation and mitigation initiatives (eg. reforestation, develop community capacity to cope with negative effects of environmental degradation, etc.)</li>\r\n	<li>Sanitation education</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><span style=\"color: #008000;\"> Social and environmental cross-cutting issues integrated in the livelihoods and </span><span style=\"color: #008000;\">environmental programmes/projects:</span></h5>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Gender equity</li>\r\n	<li>Promotion of people\'s and community\'s participation in development process</li>\r\n	<li>Capacity building and development of Community-based Organisations (CBOs)</li>\r\n	<li>Environment protection (environmental issues will be tacked by preventive protective actions and</li>\r\n	<li>Addressing the degradation that has already occured in these communities).</li>\r\n</ol>','OUR PROGRAMME','','publish','closed','open','','page-post-elements','','','2014-11-18 03:14:50','2014-11-18 03:14:50','',0,'http://themes.tielabs.com/365news/?page_id=223',0,'page','',0),(244,1,'2012-08-02 10:10:58','2012-08-02 10:10:58','<h2>Vel lorem nullam</h2>\r\nUt sit consectetuer. Aliquam velit dolor. Et ut est. Dui condimentum velit. Interdum bibendum mi arcu nonummy praesent. Suscipit platea proin. Netus commodo metus. Commodo scelerisque nibh. Cursus pede non. Lacus luctus dictum lorem ipsum nisl dolor ut pharetra. Semper sed et curabitur sed blandit. Enim vivamus hymenaeos. Donec eu lobortis morbi dis nec.\r\n<h2>Dolor nulla leo</h2>\r\nAc aliquet ut. Sociis tellus sed. Lacinia risus ornare. Magna sit ultrices. Suspendisse lacus varius. Mauris tempus sollicitudin. Mattis mi molestie. Duis enim scelerisque. Aliquam sapien urna erat sodales pellentesque. Aliquam laoreet elementum faucibus augue vivamus. Semper felis imperdiet. Metus placerat condimentum. Aliquam fringilla proin. Nunc sed in. Non magna faucibus. Metus amet blandit dictum rutrum vivamus. Urna quam aliquam. Labore tortor congue consequat elementum ut. Congue euismod mauris. Augue ultricies nascetur. Velit blandit magna. Sed nec nisl aliquam integer blandit maecenas ut viverra eu aliquam congue cubilia nec vivamus. Purus donec sit. Nullam arcu aenean. Cras adipiscing quisque nullam elit et. Nullam eveniet tempor. Accusamus amet or