 and their access to resources</li>\r\n	<li>Piloting innovative development initiatives and conducting action research</li>\r\n	<li>Advocating on livelihoods and environmental policies and implementation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4><span style=\"color: #008000;\">Our Values</span></h4><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-49\" title=\"6813233319_752a42a794_b\" src=\"http://cseed.justvelo.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/IMG_0720.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"240\" height=\"150\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ownership</li>\r\n	<li>Partnership</li>\r\n	<li>Equity</li>\r\n	<li>Transparency and Accountability</li>\r\n	<li>Efficiency</li>\r\n	<li>Sustainability</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><span style=\"color: #008000;\">Target Groups</span></h4>\r\nCSEED supports the poorest, most vulnerable and marginalized communities and individuals in the target groups\r\nwhere we work.','About us','','publish','closed','open','','about-us','','','2014-11-06 04:47:46','2014-11-06 04:47:46','',0,'http://cseed.justvelo.com/?page_id=372',0,'page','',0),(373,1,'2014-09-11 09:49:19','2014-09-11 09:49:19','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Repellat similique cupiditate, impedit hic ratione iste architecto illum, blanditiis mollitia, praesentium at quas sunt unde maiores natus autem tempora esse eius.Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Repellat similique cupiditate, impedit hic ratione iste architecto illum, blanditiis mollitia, praesentium at quas sunt unde maiores natus autem tempora esse eius.Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Repellat similique cupiditate, impedit hic ratione iste architecto illum, blanditiis mollitia, praesentium at quas sunt unde maiores natus autem tempora esse eius.Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Repellat similique cupiditate, impedit hic ratione iste architecto illum, blanditiis mollitia, praesentium at quas sunt unde maiores natus autem tempora esse eius.Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consect